OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to be chosen as
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru Leader Rhun ap Iorwerth is
OL,7,Fexpected to be chosen as the first
OL,8,Fminister on Tuesday as new Members of
OL,9,Fthe Senedd meet for the first time.
OL,11,FNew members will attend the first
OL,12,FPlenary of the seventh Senedd to elect
OL,13,Fthe presiding officer (Llywydd) and a
OL,14,Fdeputy. Once these roles are chosen,
OL,15,Fmembers will then vote on who should
OL,16,Fbe the next first minister.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
