OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to be chosen as
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FRhun ap Iorwerth is expected to become
OL,7,Fthe Senedd's official 'nominee' for
OL,8,Ffirst minister after the leader of the
OL,9,FWelsh Greens said his party will be
OL,10,Fvoting for the Plaid Cymru leader.
OL,12,FOn Sunday (10 May), Anthony Slaughter
OL,13,Fsaid Rhun ap Iorwerth has a "clear
OL,14,Fmandate" to be first minister. The
OL,15,FGreen leader and his colleague, Paul
OL,16,FRock, will both be voting in support
OL,17,Fof Mr ap Iorwerth leading the next
OL,18,FWelsh Government.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
