OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to be chosen as
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FThis will be the first time a green MS
OL,7,Fhas voted in the Senedd after the
OL,8,Fhistoric election of the two members
OL,9,Flast week.
OL,11,FOn Sunday, the two Green Senedd
OL,12,FMembers said they would support Rhun
OL,13,Fap Iorwerth, while the interim Leader
OL,14,Fof Welsh Labour Ken Skates suggested
OL,15,Fhis party's nine members will abstain
OL,16,Ffrom the vote to pick the first
OL,17,Fminister. The sole Liberal Democrat
OL,18,FMS, Jane Dodds, also said she will
OL,19,Fabstain in the vote.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
