PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778670176
OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to be chosen as
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FThose announcements have changed the
OL,7,Farithmetic in the Senedd chamber and
OL,8,Fmean there is no other way another MS
OL,9,Fcould be first minister as an
OL,10,Findividual needs more votes than are
OL,11,Fcast for all other candidates combined
OL,12,Fto win.
OL,14,FThere are 41 Reform and Conservative
OL,15,FMSs compared to the 45 that Rhun ap
OL,16,FIorwerth can now rely on.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
