OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to be chosen as
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FReform UK MS Llyr Powell said his
OL,7,Fparty will nominate their leader, Dan
OL,8,FThomas, to be first minister however
OL,9,Fthey do not have the numbers in Senedd
OL,10,Fsupport to beat Plaid Cymru's leader.
OL,12,FThis will be the first time in the
OL,13,Fhistory of devolution that the first
OL,14,Fminister will not be from Welsh
OL,15,FLabour, after their party suffered an
OL,16,Fhistoric defeat in the election.
OL,26,@nD@Ps|
