OL,3,CRhun ap Iorwerth set to be chosen as
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FThe first Plenary meeting will also
OL,7,Fselect the presiding officer (Llywydd)
OL,8,Fand deputy presiding officer. The
OL,9,FLlywydd mirrors the role of the
OL,10,Fspeaker in other parliaments. They
OL,11,Fchair meetings and remain politically
OL,12,Fimpartial.
OL,14,FThe current role holder is Plaid
OL,15,FCyrmu's Elin Jones, who will be
OL,16,Fstepping down once a new Llywydd is
OL,17,Fchosen.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
